Package org.raistlic.common.config.entity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigEntityFactory
    The interface defines contract of a config entity factory, which is capable of creating config entity beans out of some ConfigSource .
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigEntityFactories
    The class is a static factory method holder for ConfigEntityFactory interface.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ConfigConstructor
    The annotation is to mark a static factory method or constructor that is preferred to be used as the method to create a config entity instance.
    ConfigProperty
    The annotation is used to mark the members or parameters that are values to be fetched or entities to be created from the configuration context.
